(167, 1, '2014-10-22 16:12:52', '2014-10-22 08:12:52', '<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZAuoib0KPgpp2qReLp5kfUFGbmho3qTTC7ANibP1xcKeBxhEb8GSCibLegVXYaYv9BgAibhNZEOXdibFGQ/0" alt="【花子•独家】文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？" />\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》导读：任何好看的比赛都会有让人惊艳的瞬间，2014世界环球小姐大赛中国赛区一场奢华到光怪陆离的内衣秀，让全世界的看客们如浴春风、心旷神怡。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">赛后让人惊讶的是：搜狐、腾讯、乐视网、爱奇艺等无数主流媒体,一改不愿报道品牌的惯例,不惜笔墨、慷慨铺陈，有的用了版面的100%，有的用了版面的80%去报道了这个名为"美芬妮"的内衣以及其品牌CEO张丽莉。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">清丽淡雅，身材高挑，喜欢穿白衣，扎马尾，穿西服潇洒爽利，穿棉麻则安静飘逸。这就是记者眼中的张丽莉，气质高洁、人淡如菊，充满了文艺气息。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">张丽莉大学时读财经，然而她对美的执着完全可以和艺术系的人相媲美，生活中她会和一盆布艺花、一个存钱罐、一盘糖果的摆放位置较劲，只为它们能铺陈出强烈的时尚和艺术氛围。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">毕业后张丽莉选择了做调整型内衣，利用善于捕捉美丽的眼睛去挑品牌，并将这些品牌推介给SPA会所或美容院；后来，因她常到国外学习，看海外市场对内衣款式的需求，与国内外知名的打板师、内衣设计师交流，她萌生了自己设计内衣的想法。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><img title="【花子•独家】文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZAuoib0KPgpp2qReLp5kfUFGbmho3qTTC7ANibP1xcKeBxhEb8GSCibLegVXYaYv9BgAibhNZEOXdibFGQ/0" alt="【花子•独家】文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？" name="image_operate_61951412931245553" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZAuoib0KPgpp2qReLp5kfUFGbmho3qTTC7ANibP1xcKeBxhEb8GSCibLegVXYaYv9BgAibhNZEOXdibFGQ/0" data-s="300,640" data-ratio="0.6673267326732674" data-w="" /></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">在大多数人的意识里，调整型内衣是单调的、呆板的、不舒服的，但在张丽莉心里调整型内衣既代表女人希望变美的内在诉求，又是表现女人外在美的重磅武器。本着内外兼修的原则，她设计的调整型内衣，华丽美艳又兼具调整身形的功能，深受顾客欢迎，美芬妮品牌在她的支撑下做得风生水起。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">当然，经营中有许多困难，对不善言辞的张丽莉来说，最主要的一个困难是作为企业的领导者，站在台上说场面话，介绍自家的东西如何好。后来她想了一个好办法，每当要说场面话她就用“内衣秀”来取代。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">       金发碧眼的外国模特，穿着她设计的内衣，在T台上风情万种的一走，大家的眼球被齐刷刷地抓过去。内衣好不好，不用说，看一眼全知道。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">随着经验的累积，美芬妮的秀场越来越大，张丽莉掌控秀场的能力越来越强。也许前一刻她还是邻家妹妹的样子，站在人群中斯文柔弱，我见犹怜；但一开始工作，即使是10000人的场子她也能指挥若定、条理分明。她用美丽的方式，打破了行业传统的项目运作方式。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>不拘一格的美丽灵感“电”到媒体</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">2014环球小姐大赛之前，张丽莉在朋友的鼓励下，怀着一颗惴惴不安的心向羽西自荐美芬妮。这么大的人物会看上自己的作品吗？况且欧洲最知名的内衣品牌与羽西已经谈了很久。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">要不是知道羽西关心慈善、注重内在美，与自己在心灵上无比贴近，她简直没勇气完成自荐的过程。令人惊讶的是，羽西没有过多犹豫，环球小姐选择搭档才不管大牌不大牌，羽西只有一个标准，那就是要有个性、要十分美丽。而美芬妮长久以来呈现的状态正是个性的、奇异的，不按套路出牌的时尚与美丽。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">签完约，按理双方会交流更多，但在一次采访中，羽西好奇地提到：这个叫张丽莉的女孩子消失了。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">张丽莉去哪了？3个半月的时间，她都留在上海哪也没去，一向小资的她不呼朋唤友聚会了，一天24小时除了吃饭和睡觉只做一件事，那就是设计、设计、设计！</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">用成绩说话，用作品代言自己，是张丽莉的做事方式。在美芬妮之前国内从未有一家内衣品牌走上国际舞台，要么不做、要么做好的性格让她充满了使命感；另外，有一件严肃的事，她告诉自己一定要对得起这么重要的人对自己的信任，她要用作品去打动羽西。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">环球小姐大赛有个惯例，就是走秀之前，会有国际水准的拍摄团队前来拍纪录片，记录创作者的纠结和辛苦，张丽莉二话不说就拒绝了，争分夺秒，她针对每一位参赛小姐的身材、个性和风格，设计出几十套美丽内衣，后来精选出14套在台上参赛。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">当身穿美芬妮内衣的环球小姐逐一登台，这场中国元素与时尚前沿混搭的视觉盛宴，让现场的掌声和男人肾上腺素一路飙升，连女人都在惊叹：“天呐！内衣还可以做得这么奢华！”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;" align="center"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=48d103940102v73u&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/001kFWV6zy6MHNqjjZWf4" target="_blank"> </a></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">赛后搜狐、腾讯、乐视网、爱奇艺等无数主流媒体，一改不愿报道品牌的惯例，不惜笔墨、慷慨铺陈，有的用了版面的100%，有的用了版面的80%去报道了这个叫美芬妮的内衣，以及该品牌CEO张丽莉。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">感恩是金，羽西是张丽莉生命中的贵人，她将张丽莉不拘一格的美丽灵感在最璀璨的舞台上呈现；而张丽莉正是用这颗感恩的心去做，让这个璀璨的舞台更加迷人。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>海阔凭鱼跃，美芬妮张开了天使之翼</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">刹那光鲜定格在岁月，美女CEO向着更大的舞台果敢前进。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">在2014广东美博会上，慕名来买美芬妮的人大多是美业同行，很多人一出手就是十几万、几十万地为自己购进，为美容会所批量购进的上百万货品，各个都是大手笔。针对为自己买内衣的顾客，有时张丽莉会好心地提醒：“你试了吗？我觉得某些款式并不完全适合你。”对方会欣喜地回答：“试了，都非常喜欢。”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">当一个品牌的环境和所有的文化呈现被人们真心欣赏时，一切消费都不在话下。当然，在环球小姐的带动下，美芬妮的粉丝不仅在国内，也不仅在美容行业，她已张开天使之翼，飞到了世界时尚圈、名媛圈……</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">国庆节期间，在夏威夷国际电影节上，张丽莉与众多明星一起出席，羽西体贴地将她引荐给国外知名的媒体、名媛，并详细地介绍了她在环球小姐大赛中国赛区的优秀表现。当时，夏威夷、纽约等城市最大的房地产商、顶级的商场老板都在场，当即提议在一些高级的场合引进美芬妮。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">美芬妮的天使之翼即将在美国展翅，而以谦卑勤勉的美业人的身份进军国际时尚圈，张丽莉的路才刚刚开始。我们期待春节前环球小姐总决赛之际，她给大家带来更多惊喜。</p>', '文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%96%87%e8%89%ba%e8%8c%83%e7%be%8e%e5%a5%b3ceo%e5%bc%a0%e4%b8%bd%e8%8e%89%ef%bc%9a%e6%88%91%e5%87%ad%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e6%89%93%e5%8a%a8%e4%ba%86%e7%be%bd%e8%a5%bf%ef%bc%9f', '', '', '2014-10-22 16:12:52', '2014-10-22 08:12:52', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.129/wp/?p=167', 0, 'post', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(168, 1, '2014-10-22 16:12:52', '2014-10-22 08:12:52', '<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZAuoib0KPgpp2qReLp5kfUFGbmho3qTTC7ANibP1xcKeBxhEb8GSCibLegVXYaYv9BgAibhNZEOXdibFGQ/0" alt="【花子•独家】文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？" />\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》导读：任何好看的比赛都会有让人惊艳的瞬间，2014世界环球小姐大赛中国赛区一场奢华到光怪陆离的内衣秀，让全世界的看客们如浴春风、心旷神怡。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">赛后让人惊讶的是：搜狐、腾讯、乐视网、爱奇艺等无数主流媒体,一改不愿报道品牌的惯例,不惜笔墨、慷慨铺陈，有的用了版面的100%，有的用了版面的80%去报道了这个名为"美芬妮"的内衣以及其品牌CEO张丽莉。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">清丽淡雅，身材高挑，喜欢穿白衣，扎马尾，穿西服潇洒爽利，穿棉麻则安静飘逸。这就是记者眼中的张丽莉，气质高洁、人淡如菊，充满了文艺气息。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">张丽莉大学时读财经，然而她对美的执着完全可以和艺术系的人相媲美，生活中她会和一盆布艺花、一个存钱罐、一盘糖果的摆放位置较劲，只为它们能铺陈出强烈的时尚和艺术氛围。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">毕业后张丽莉选择了做调整型内衣，利用善于捕捉美丽的眼睛去挑品牌，并将这些品牌推介给SPA会所或美容院；后来，因她常到国外学习，看海外市场对内衣款式的需求，与国内外知名的打板师、内衣设计师交流，她萌生了自己设计内衣的想法。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><img title="【花子•独家】文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZAuoib0KPgpp2qReLp5kfUFGbmho3qTTC7ANibP1xcKeBxhEb8GSCibLegVXYaYv9BgAibhNZEOXdibFGQ/0" alt="【花子•独家】文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？" name="image_operate_61951412931245553" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZAuoib0KPgpp2qReLp5kfUFGbmho3qTTC7ANibP1xcKeBxhEb8GSCibLegVXYaYv9BgAibhNZEOXdibFGQ/0" data-s="300,640" data-ratio="0.6673267326732674" data-w="" /></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">在大多数人的意识里，调整型内衣是单调的、呆板的、不舒服的，但在张丽莉心里调整型内衣既代表女人希望变美的内在诉求，又是表现女人外在美的重磅武器。本着内外兼修的原则，她设计的调整型内衣，华丽美艳又兼具调整身形的功能，深受顾客欢迎，美芬妮品牌在她的支撑下做得风生水起。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">当然，经营中有许多困难，对不善言辞的张丽莉来说，最主要的一个困难是作为企业的领导者，站在台上说场面话，介绍自家的东西如何好。后来她想了一个好办法，每当要说场面话她就用“内衣秀”来取代。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">       金发碧眼的外国模特，穿着她设计的内衣，在T台上风情万种的一走，大家的眼球被齐刷刷地抓过去。内衣好不好，不用说，看一眼全知道。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">随着经验的累积，美芬妮的秀场越来越大，张丽莉掌控秀场的能力越来越强。也许前一刻她还是邻家妹妹的样子，站在人群中斯文柔弱，我见犹怜；但一开始工作，即使是10000人的场子她也能指挥若定、条理分明。她用美丽的方式，打破了行业传统的项目运作方式。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>不拘一格的美丽灵感“电”到媒体</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">2014环球小姐大赛之前，张丽莉在朋友的鼓励下，怀着一颗惴惴不安的心向羽西自荐美芬妮。这么大的人物会看上自己的作品吗？况且欧洲最知名的内衣品牌与羽西已经谈了很久。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">要不是知道羽西关心慈善、注重内在美，与自己在心灵上无比贴近，她简直没勇气完成自荐的过程。令人惊讶的是，羽西没有过多犹豫，环球小姐选择搭档才不管大牌不大牌，羽西只有一个标准，那就是要有个性、要十分美丽。而美芬妮长久以来呈现的状态正是个性的、奇异的，不按套路出牌的时尚与美丽。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">签完约，按理双方会交流更多，但在一次采访中，羽西好奇地提到：这个叫张丽莉的女孩子消失了。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">张丽莉去哪了？3个半月的时间，她都留在上海哪也没去，一向小资的她不呼朋唤友聚会了，一天24小时除了吃饭和睡觉只做一件事，那就是设计、设计、设计！</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">用成绩说话，用作品代言自己，是张丽莉的做事方式。在美芬妮之前国内从未有一家内衣品牌走上国际舞台，要么不做、要么做好的性格让她充满了使命感；另外，有一件严肃的事，她告诉自己一定要对得起这么重要的人对自己的信任，她要用作品去打动羽西。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">环球小姐大赛有个惯例，就是走秀之前，会有国际水准的拍摄团队前来拍纪录片，记录创作者的纠结和辛苦，张丽莉二话不说就拒绝了，争分夺秒，她针对每一位参赛小姐的身材、个性和风格，设计出几十套美丽内衣，后来精选出14套在台上参赛。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">当身穿美芬妮内衣的环球小姐逐一登台，这场中国元素与时尚前沿混搭的视觉盛宴，让现场的掌声和男人肾上腺素一路飙升，连女人都在惊叹：“天呐！内衣还可以做得这么奢华！”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;" align="center"><a href="http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=48d103940102v73u&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/001kFWV6zy6MHNqjjZWf4" target="_blank"> </a></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">赛后搜狐、腾讯、乐视网、爱奇艺等无数主流媒体，一改不愿报道品牌的惯例，不惜笔墨、慷慨铺陈，有的用了版面的100%，有的用了版面的80%去报道了这个叫美芬妮的内衣，以及该品牌CEO张丽莉。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">感恩是金，羽西是张丽莉生命中的贵人，她将张丽莉不拘一格的美丽灵感在最璀璨的舞台上呈现；而张丽莉正是用这颗感恩的心去做，让这个璀璨的舞台更加迷人。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>海阔凭鱼跃，美芬妮张开了天使之翼</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">刹那光鲜定格在岁月，美女CEO向着更大的舞台果敢前进。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">在2014广东美博会上，慕名来买美芬妮的人大多是美业同行，很多人一出手就是十几万、几十万地为自己购进，为美容会所批量购进的上百万货品，各个都是大手笔。针对为自己买内衣的顾客，有时张丽莉会好心地提醒：“你试了吗？我觉得某些款式并不完全适合你。”对方会欣喜地回答：“试了，都非常喜欢。”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">当一个品牌的环境和所有的文化呈现被人们真心欣赏时，一切消费都不在话下。当然，在环球小姐的带动下，美芬妮的粉丝不仅在国内，也不仅在美容行业，她已张开天使之翼，飞到了世界时尚圈、名媛圈……</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">国庆节期间，在夏威夷国际电影节上，张丽莉与众多明星一起出席，羽西体贴地将她引荐给国外知名的媒体、名媛，并详细地介绍了她在环球小姐大赛中国赛区的优秀表现。当时，夏威夷、纽约等城市最大的房地产商、顶级的商场老板都在场，当即提议在一些高级的场合引进美芬妮。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">美芬妮的天使之翼即将在美国展翅，而以谦卑勤勉的美业人的身份进军国际时尚圈，张丽莉的路才刚刚开始。我们期待春节前环球小姐总决赛之际，她给大家带来更多惊喜。</p>', '文艺范美女CEO张丽莉：我凭什么打动了羽西？', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '167-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-22 16:12:52', '2014-10-22 08:12:52', '', 167, 'http://192.168.1.129/wp/?p=168', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(169, 1, '2014-10-22 16:17:44', '2014-10-22 08:17:44', '<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55ghiboDWCR5g11x9dGnjVz6Ky0JNVjlOmcydjGZHO0HhNGwLUY8cGk5PA/0" alt="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" />\r\n<p style="font: 14px/23px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》导读：当初只是抱着“看一看”的心态去招商会，没想到5分钟后自己就被俘虏，成为现场第一个签单的人。到底是什么让他如此“当机立断”？一起来听听安徽兄和弟化妆品商贸有限公司总经理闵晓非的精彩分享。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">第一个吃螃蟹的人</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">5月11日，听朋友说伏今非在广州有一场大型招商会，闵晓非抱着“去看一看”的心态赶到会场。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">此时会场已是座无虚席，讲课也到了最精彩的部分。用闵晓非自己的话，就是“简单5分钟，我就感受到了伏今非老师强大的磁场，讲的东西非常落地”。因此，虽然去得晚，闵晓非却成了当天第一个签单的人。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">事实证明，第一个吃螃蟹的人收获是巨大的。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">公司下面有70多家店，每家店反应都很好，业绩收入均有大幅增长。一个已经做了10多年的老店，去年整年的业绩还只是150万，今年短短60天就做到了260万。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><img title="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gj6ic1fbd4LPfC7EBHdWpgib8ib6RfdYgbG3j4ZzZFWHABK3wHPCvojDdg/0" alt="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" width="313" height="397" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gj6ic1fbd4LPfC7EBHdWpgib8ib6RfdYgbG3j4ZzZFWHABK3wHPCvojDdg/0" data-s="300,640" data-ratio="1.3432835820895523" data-w="268" /></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">重视顾客的感觉</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">太平陈榆店之前客情做得一直不太好，美容师自己也找不出顾客流失的原因，无从下手干着急。通过殿堂营销的学习，他们意识到顾客到店消费买的是感觉，而这种感觉源于服务的每一个小细节，在这里能得到最大的尊重和回娘家的感觉。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">在翻阅顾客资料时，一位美容师发现一名顾客体内长期积有湿寒，且已经有段时间没到店了。于是她特地回老家带来了几斤绿豆，跑到顾客楼下，电话里得知对方在会客不便打扰，便在楼下守候。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">恰好此时下起了小雨，门外也没有一个很好的遮雨地方，于是美容师就在半遮半淋雨的状态下等候了3个小时。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">直到顾客送客出门时才发现了这位淋得一身湿的小姑娘，看着小姑娘怀里捧着的一袋子绿豆，又听明来意，顾客感动得一塌糊涂，赶紧将小姑娘请到家里，既是做饭又是煮姜汤。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">结果可想而知，这位顾客又成了店里的常客。当天家里的那位客人也将小姑娘的行为看在眼里，惊讶地夸赞：“这是哪家店的小姑娘，这么体贴？”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><img title="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gf1HbmmEHDDJ1xBloicdoiaTluk7pfqeJIn8h4Fib3P2T4ejShUzR32v4Q/0" alt="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" width="227" height="345" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gf1HbmmEHDDJ1xBloicdoiaTluk7pfqeJIn8h4Fib3P2T4ejShUzR32v4Q/0" data-s="300,640" data-ratio="1.4229249011857707" data-w="253" /></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">让员工找到感觉</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">安徽毫州绿色总店店长刘婷婷分享说，通过学习殿堂营销不仅看到服务和业绩的变化，同时也看到了店里团队的改变。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">由于美容师的年龄普遍偏小，工作较懒惰，尤其是夏天天气炎热，精神懒散，工作也做不好，需要加班时总会抱怨：“怎么又要加班？”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">接受殿堂培训后，团队配合“八卦”、“演戏”，被吊足胃口的顾客忍不住要问要买。之后再做感恩服务，给顾客的“贴心一句话”，美容师之间、美容师和顾客之间，互动越来越多，也变得越来越好玩。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">既好玩又能销售，刘婷婷发现，小姑娘们不再“蔫了吧唧”的了。激情和榜样的力量感染着每一个人，不论新老员工，整个团队变得激情昂扬，也不再把加班当成负担。每个人都清楚地知道自己的计划和目标，之前不太主动的员工也开始愿意开口说话，积极主动地分析自己的客户。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">刘婷婷说，之前出一个5万和10万的单都觉得很了不起，现在成单10万、20万都很常见，看到现在的成绩让她对全年目标有了100%的信心。</p>', '是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！ ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%98%af%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88%e8%ae%a9%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86%e5%95%86%e5%bd%93%e6%9c%ba%e7%ab%8b%e6%96%ad%ef%bc%8c%e6%88%90%e4%b8%ba%e7%8e%b0%e5%9c%ba%e7%ad%be%e5%8d%95%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e4%ba%ba%ef%bc%9f', '', '', '2014-10-22 16:17:44', '2014-10-22 08:17:44', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.129/wp/?p=169', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(170, 1, '2014-10-22 16:17:44', '2014-10-22 08:17:44', '<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55ghiboDWCR5g11x9dGnjVz6Ky0JNVjlOmcydjGZHO0HhNGwLUY8cGk5PA/0" alt="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" />\r\n<p style="font: 14px/23px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》导读：当初只是抱着“看一看”的心态去招商会，没想到5分钟后自己就被俘虏，成为现场第一个签单的人。到底是什么让他如此“当机立断”？一起来听听安徽兄和弟化妆品商贸有限公司总经理闵晓非的精彩分享。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">第一个吃螃蟹的人</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">5月11日，听朋友说伏今非在广州有一场大型招商会，闵晓非抱着“去看一看”的心态赶到会场。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">此时会场已是座无虚席，讲课也到了最精彩的部分。用闵晓非自己的话，就是“简单5分钟，我就感受到了伏今非老师强大的磁场，讲的东西非常落地”。因此，虽然去得晚，闵晓非却成了当天第一个签单的人。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">事实证明，第一个吃螃蟹的人收获是巨大的。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">公司下面有70多家店，每家店反应都很好，业绩收入均有大幅增长。一个已经做了10多年的老店，去年整年的业绩还只是150万，今年短短60天就做到了260万。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><img title="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gj6ic1fbd4LPfC7EBHdWpgib8ib6RfdYgbG3j4ZzZFWHABK3wHPCvojDdg/0" alt="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" width="313" height="397" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gj6ic1fbd4LPfC7EBHdWpgib8ib6RfdYgbG3j4ZzZFWHABK3wHPCvojDdg/0" data-s="300,640" data-ratio="1.3432835820895523" data-w="268" /></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">重视顾客的感觉</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">太平陈榆店之前客情做得一直不太好，美容师自己也找不出顾客流失的原因，无从下手干着急。通过殿堂营销的学习，他们意识到顾客到店消费买的是感觉，而这种感觉源于服务的每一个小细节，在这里能得到最大的尊重和回娘家的感觉。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">在翻阅顾客资料时，一位美容师发现一名顾客体内长期积有湿寒，且已经有段时间没到店了。于是她特地回老家带来了几斤绿豆，跑到顾客楼下，电话里得知对方在会客不便打扰，便在楼下守候。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">恰好此时下起了小雨，门外也没有一个很好的遮雨地方，于是美容师就在半遮半淋雨的状态下等候了3个小时。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">直到顾客送客出门时才发现了这位淋得一身湿的小姑娘，看着小姑娘怀里捧着的一袋子绿豆，又听明来意，顾客感动得一塌糊涂，赶紧将小姑娘请到家里，既是做饭又是煮姜汤。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">结果可想而知，这位顾客又成了店里的常客。当天家里的那位客人也将小姑娘的行为看在眼里，惊讶地夸赞：“这是哪家店的小姑娘，这么体贴？”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/21px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><img title="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gf1HbmmEHDDJ1xBloicdoiaTluk7pfqeJIn8h4Fib3P2T4ejShUzR32v4Q/0" alt="【花子•独家】是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！" width="227" height="345" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZCnag6icialMopfvjDho1q55gf1HbmmEHDDJ1xBloicdoiaTluk7pfqeJIn8h4Fib3P2T4ejShUzR32v4Q/0" data-s="300,640" data-ratio="1.4229249011857707" data-w="253" /></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">让员工找到感觉</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">安徽毫州绿色总店店长刘婷婷分享说，通过学习殿堂营销不仅看到服务和业绩的变化，同时也看到了店里团队的改变。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">由于美容师的年龄普遍偏小，工作较懒惰，尤其是夏天天气炎热，精神懒散，工作也做不好，需要加班时总会抱怨：“怎么又要加班？”</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">接受殿堂培训后，团队配合“八卦”、“演戏”，被吊足胃口的顾客忍不住要问要买。之后再做感恩服务，给顾客的“贴心一句话”，美容师之间、美容师和顾客之间，互动越来越多，也变得越来越好玩。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">既好玩又能销售，刘婷婷发现，小姑娘们不再“蔫了吧唧”的了。激情和榜样的力量感染着每一个人，不论新老员工，整个团队变得激情昂扬，也不再把加班当成负担。每个人都清楚地知道自己的计划和目标，之前不太主动的员工也开始愿意开口说话，积极主动地分析自己的客户。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 32px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">刘婷婷说，之前出一个5万和10万的单都觉得很了不起，现在成单10万、20万都很常见，看到现在的成绩让她对全年目标有了100%的信心。</p>', '是什么让代理商当机立断，成为现场签单第一人？点这里！ ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '169-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-22 16:17:44', '2014-10-22 08:17:44', '', 169, 'http://192.168.1.129/wp/?p=170', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(171, 1, '2014-10-22 16:26:26', '2014-10-22 08:26:26', '<img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/JW3RjibVsaZC8BHicxVsibVc7SicNgNocssowYANLFqKUanDQLHUJiaquPgmvNF04nibM2JgxmiafQLdckiaia7VHmic8BqA/0" alt="【花子•独家】李宝亮：一天十几次在自己脸上试产品，不做白鼠不成精" />\r\n<p style="font: 14px/23px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>《花子直播间》导读：</strong>基因工程技术让基因美容迈入“双核”时代，《花子直播间》对话广州巨子生物科技有限公司总经理李宝亮，揭开基因美容疗法的神秘面纱。从一天十几次做脸体验效果，到以爱之名的企业文化，李宝亮带领我们一起看看高端技术背后的精英队伍。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>员工考核最后一环：在老板脸上试产品</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》：据了解，巨子在9月初举办了“高科美塑”第一届技能大赛，大赛的初衷是什么？</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>李宝亮：</strong>技术服务是公司的命脉，成熟、稳定的技术是第一生产力，所以巨子对技术的要求很高。在我们公司，考核员工的最后一个环节是在我的脸上试练。有时候一天下来，我的脸要被做十几次，我这张角质层超厚的老脸是现身说法，也算是对产品破坏性的一种实验。如果我一天做十几次都没有问题，那么顾客就更加没有后顾之忧了。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">技能大赛就是专门针对专业版块进行的比拼，比赛由主题演讲、现场操作和专业知识考核3部分组成的。这种形式的赛制是对员工技术潜能的一种挖掘，尽量做到精益求精，我相信，没有最好，只有更好。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>以爱之名，为员工父母支付养老金</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》：巨子生物建立以“爱”为首的企业文化，您对此是如何理解的？</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>李宝亮：</strong>市场压力大，整个时代都充斥着躁动不安的情绪。生活在其中，很容易迷失自己，也忽略了很多东西。人需要很多很多的力量来支撑，而爱就拥有这样的力量。唯独有爱，才能恒久。我想，人可能就是为爱服务的。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">员工转正之后，公司会为员工父母交养老金，而且每年都有提高。在我看来，这也是爱的一种方式，让每个员工都感觉到不是自己一个人在战斗，而是时时刻刻置身于一个大的集体中。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》：关于“爱让我们在一起”2014团队年中培训旅游季，您能否跟我们分享一下趣事？</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>李宝亮：</strong>为期一周的培训旅游季，发生了很多趣事。钱多多的抓钱舞、背靠背心贴心的互动现场、写满一整面墙的爱心贴纸……让我印象最深刻、最感动的就是员工之间互相洗脚按摩，当时很多人都哭了。一家人，真的就是一家人。不只是自我突破，也是让他们体会到用劳动所传递出来的爱心，无形中拉近了距离。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: center; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>基因美容迈入“双核”时代</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">《花子直播间》：贵公司以基因工程技术为基点在美容疗法上有什么样的成果？</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong>李宝亮：</strong>巨子生物整合基因工程药物国家工程研究中心、暨南大学分子生物研究中心，这两个顶级生物技术研发平台的最新基因美容科研成果——复合活性多肽，首创“双核”基因美容疗法，让基因美容迈入“双核”时代。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Thermage抗衰老的射频仪器和高科美塑是我们现在的主打产品，后期也会朝生物基因美容、抗衰老等项目上进一步发展。</p>\r\n<p style="font: 14px/27px ''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Helvetica Neue'', SimSun; list-style: none; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; text-align: left; color: #494949; text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; -ms-word-break: normal; -ms-word-wrap: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #edf2ca; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">马云说，下一个首富会出现在健康产业。美容行业就属于健康产业，国内的市场环境广，随着年龄逐渐老化的发展趋势，抗衰老项目必然是美容界不可逆转的新潮流。</p>', '李宝亮：一天十几次在自己脸上试产品，不做白鼠不成精 ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%9d%8e%e5%ae%9d%e4%ba%ae%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%80%e5%a4%a9%e5%8d%81%e5%87%a0%e6%ac%a1%e5%9c%a8%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1%e8%84%b8%e4%b8%8a%e8%af%95%e4%ba%a7%e5%93%81%ef%bc%8c%e4%b8%8d%e5%81%9a%e7%99%bd%e9%bc%a0', '', '', '2014-10-22 16:26:26', '2014-10-22 08:26:26', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.129/wp/?p=171', 0, 'post', '', 0),
